        <item>
            <title>Version 0.5.0</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <h2>What's New in 0.5.0</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Customize up to 4 Quick Actions in the Control Center for one-tap access to your favorite features.</li>
                        <li>Presets now save per-preset settings for Translation, Conversation Mode, Date Context, and Build & Verify.</li>
                        <li>Notes and Journal sidebars are now resizable — drag to your preferred width.</li>
                        <li>A subtle usage gauge appears when you're approaching your weekly limit.</li>
                        <li>Expanded in-app help for the Screenshot Gallery with tips on filtering, sorting, and sharing.</li>
                        <li>Stability and performance improvements.</li>
